Text:
You`re my man!

Really like this bootlegs with the King!

Thanks!
Just one small note, this is actually the August 12th 1972 dinner show. The real August 11th 1972 dinner show is released on the FTD label as 'Elvis Summer Festival'.

Great upload and thanks for sharing.  It's a shame there aren't more people seeding this great concert 'cos it took me quite a while to get!  I will seed for as long as I can.

Nicholas
